description: Live in luxury @ Dahlgren Hall, South Boston's premier boutique elevator building. This quiet & private corner unit offers deeded garage parking & access to the neighborhood's best roofdeck w/clubhouse, including kitchen & lounge! Easy elevator access from heated garage pkg to this sunlit contemporary condo. Designer kitchen w/high end appliances, modern waterfall island & custom Philips Hue under cabinet lighting. Open layout to dining area w/adjacent prvt balcony & spacious living room. Impressive primary suite w/gas fireplace, large custom walk-in closet & en suite master bath. King-size 2nd bed w/built out closet to maximize storage. Spacious & beautifully finished full 2nd/guest bathroom w/glass doors, smart thermostat, the newest smart tech home features, central A/C (new w/ warranty), in-unit laundry, plus massive, private storage room - can be converted to a private gym/home office! Close to Seaport, Castle Island, Carson Beach, Lawn on D, & countless world class restaurants.
